Project Name - Calculator

This project is a simple calculator built with HTML, CSS (using grid layout), and JavaScript. The calculator has basic arithmetic operations 
like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. 

Getting Started
To run the project, simply open the index.html file in your web browser.

Prerequisites
To run this project, you will need a web browser.

Built With
1. HTML
2. CSS (using grid layout)
3. JavaScript

Features
1. Basic arithmetic operations
2. Responsive design

How to Use
1. Enter a number using the number buttons
2. Select an arithmetic operation
3. Enter a second number
4. Press the equals button to see the result
5. To clear the input, press the clear button(AC).
